data.description: Welcome home to this spectacular 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom haven! Nestled in a prime location near the bridge to Sioux City with seamless access to I-29, this residence is the epitome of comfort and convenience. Step inside and discover a truly remarkable feature—this home is "zero-entry" on the main level, meaning absolutely no stairs on any of the 5 doors accessing the home or in the master bedroom shower. Imagine the ease of everyday living with main floor laundry, ensuring practicality at its finest. Built on a patio slab, rest easy knowing that water issues in the basement will never be an issue. Yet, storage abounds with generously sized closets throughout and an additional storage attic space upstairs. The 2-car oversized HEATED garage is a hobbyist's dream, boasting a "workshop" layout and an additional tiled bonus space ideal for a home gym or home based office. The exterior delights with a brand-new 6 ft. vinyl privacy fence courtesy of American Fence, providing a serene retreat. The roof, replaced in 2017 with a transferable lifetime warranty, along with new gutters, ensures worry-free living. Revel in the comfort of a new furnace and central A/C units installed in 2015, complemented by regular seasonal service for optimal performance. A standout feature is the four seasons room—an incredible bonus that could serve as a hot tub and entertaining haven or easily transformed into a 5th bedroom. The thoughtful owners have converted the under-stair storage into an 11x4 Taj Mahal for their fur babies, a charming touch that could adapt to your needs, whether keeping it the same, as a cozy office space or your very own Harry Potter reading room! For the past 11 years, the current owners have poured their heart into renovations, leaving you with nothing to do but move in and enjoy the seamless blend of style and functionality. This property is zoned C2 which means it is residential zoning but with the opportunity to run a home based business out of it immediately!
